Developer Terms of Use
des: TMNA Team members at HQ Plano TX can schedule service for company leased car using Toyota MyService Skill. Simply say "Alexa ask Toyota My Service to schedule appointment". If you want to check service alerts of your vehicle, you can things like "Alexa ask Toyota My Service what's wrong with my car".
